OL,3,CCost of fixing pothole-damaged cars
OL,4,Chits record high
OL,6,FThe total cost of repairing vehicles
OL,7,Fdamaged by potholes hit #579m last
OL,8,Fyear.
OL,10,FThat is compared with #474 million
OL,11,Fduring the previous 12 months and is
OL,12,Fthe highest total on record.
OL,14,FCommon problems caused by potholes
OL,15,Finclude damaged shock absorbers,
OL,16,Fbroken suspension springs and
OL,17,Fdistorted wheels.
