OL,3,CCost of fixing pothole-damaged cars
OL,4,Chits record high
OL,6,FThe increased costs were caused by a
OL,7,Fleap in the average repair bills from
OL,8,F#250 to #300, despite 4,372 fewer
OL,9,Fincidents.
OL,11,FThe AA attributed the rise in average
OL,12,Frepair costs to inflation, more
OL,13,Fadvanced technology in cars and
OL,14,Fshortages of spare parts.
OL,16,FThe new figures were released as part
OL,17,Fof National Pothole Day, which
OL,18,Fcampaign groups marked by urging local
OL,19,Fauthorities to implement permanent
OL,20,Frepairs rather than "patch and run"
OL,21,Fpolicies.
