OL,3,CCost of fixing pothole-damaged cars
OL,4,Chits record high
OL,6,FThe recent cold weather also caused
OL,7,Fone of its busiest periods for five
OL,8,Fyears, which the RAC called an
OL,9,F"unwelcome trend" which could
OL,10,F"continue into 2025".
