OL,3,CCost of fixing pothole-damaged cars
OL,4,Chits record high
OL,6,FThe Department for Transport
OL,7,Fpreviously said it will make sure
OL,8,Fhighway authorities "spend the money
OL,9,Fwisely" and deliver "proactive
OL,10,Fmaintenance" before potholes start to
OL,11,Fform.
OL,13,FA quarter of the increased funding
OL,14,Fwill be held back until authorities
OL,15,Fhave demonstrated they are using it
OL,16,Fwell.
OL,18,FThe cost of bringing pothole-plagued
OL,19,Flocal roads in England and Wales up to
OL,20,Fscratch has been estimated at #16.3
OL,21,Fbillion.
